      "text": [
        "2049 - وَ قَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «لاَ وِصَالَ فِي صِيَامٍ وَ لاَ صَمْتَ يَوْماً إِلَى اَللَّيْلِ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2049 - Imam (as) said:\n\"There is no continuous fasting (wisal) in fasting, nor remaining silent for a day until night.\""
        ]
      }
    }
  },
